llistener" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h4><code>(event: <a href="#accellistenerevent">AccelListenerEvent</a>): void</code><h4 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_3ly5" id="orientationlistener">OrientationListener<a aria-hidden="true" class="hash-link" href="#orientationlistener" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h4><code>(event: <a href="#rotationrate">RotationRate</a>): void</code><h4 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_3ly5" id="orientationlistenerevent">OrientationListenerEvent<a aria-hidden="true" class="hash-link" href="#orientationlistenerevent" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h4><a href="#rotationrate">RotationRate</a></docgen-api></div><footer class="theme-doc-footer docusaurus-mt-lg"><div class="theme-doc-footer-edit-meta-row row"><div class="col"><a href="https://github.com/ionic-team/capacitor-plugins/edit/main/motion/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="theme-edit-this-page"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-edit iconEdit_PItR"><path d="M7 0C3.13438 0 0 3.21563 0 7.17813C0 10.35 2.00625 13.0375 4.7875 13.9875C4.83125 13.9969 4.86875 14 4.90625 14C5.16563 14 5.26562 13.8094 5.26562 13.6438C5.26562 13.4719 5.25938 13.0219 5.25625 12.4219C4.99375 12.4812 4.75938 12.5063 4.55 12.5063C3.20313 12.5063 2.89687 11.4594 2.89687 11.4594C2.57812 10.6313 2.11875 10.4094 2.11875 10.4094C1.50938 9.98125 2.11562 9.96875 2.1625 9.96875H2.16563C2.86875 10.0312 3.2375 10.7125 3.2375 10.7125C3.5875 11.325 4.05625 11.4969 4.475 11.4969C4.80312 11.4969 5.1 11.3906 5.275 11.3094C5.3375 10.8469 5.51875 10.5312 5.71875 10.35C4.16563 10.1688 2.53125 9.55313 2.53125 6.80312C2.53125 6.01875 2.80312 5.37813 3.25 4.87813C3.17812 4.69688 2.9375 3.96563 3.31875 2.97813C3.31875 2.97813 3.36875 2.9625 3.475 2.9625C3.72812 2.9625 4.3 3.05937 5.24375 3.71562C5.80312 3.55625 6.4 3.47812 6.99687 3.475C7.59062 3.47812 8.19063 3.55625 8.75 3.71562C9.69375 3.05937 1